# Trivy ignore list. Add CVE IDs here when:
#   - the upstream fix is not yet released, or
#   - the path is unreachable in our deployment, or
#   - we have a compensating control documented elsewhere.
#
# Format: one CVE / advisory ID per line, blank lines and `#` comments allowed.
# Always include a comment explaining the rationale and an expiry date.
#
# Example:
# CVE-2024-XXXXX  # unreachable: only triggered by malicious admin input; revisit 2026-12-01
